\par
If Rich Text Box is present with some text and has not been saved to a file (text file doesn't exists), show that "Do you wish to save changes to this text"?, when clicking the new button\b\par
    User clicks Yes -> Save As Dialog Open -> User Saves -> New Text Editor \par
   User clicks No -> Don't Save the text -> New Text Editor\par
   User clicks Cancel -> Go back to the application or screen where text present\par
\b0\par
\i\fs34 AND\i0\fs24\par
\par
