\par
If Rich Tex Box is present with text and the latest changes has not yet been saved to a current existing file, it will prompt the user with MessageBox "Do you want to save changes to the \{currentFile\}" which if\par
       \b User clicks Yes -> Save the file -> New Text Editor\par
      User clicks No -> Don't Save the File ->New Text Editor\par
      User clicks Cancel -> Go back to the application or screen\par
